agentData.mission: Implement the three experiments as a single reproducible Jupyter notebook (and companion Python modules) using Python 3.11+ and SymPy: include (A) analytic derivations (SymPy symbolic steps), (B) numeric implementations (NumPy/SciPy), (C) parameter sweep harness, (D) automated unit tests (pytest-compatible), and (E) plotting code. Add save/load hooks to export figures (PNG/SVG) and CSV results.
